Set Up Third-Party Data for Segment Intelligence

Connect your third-party data to view your campaign delivery and performance metrics in the Segment Intelligence dashboard.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience	Available in: Enterprise and Unlimited Editions
Select a Third-Party Connection for Segment Intelligence
Choose a connection for your third-party data. You can then create a data stream to display your data in the dashboard.
Create a Meta Ads Data Stream for Segment Intelligence
To connect your Meta Ads data, create a data stream and then map the fields in Data Cloud
Create a Google Ads Data Stream for Segment Intelligence
To connect your Google Ads data, create a data stream and then map the fields in Data Cloud
Create the Data Cloud Objects to Connect Third-Party Data
Use the Segment Intelligence setup flow to add the required data model objects (DMOs), and map the data streams to the DMOs for Google Ads and Meta Ads data.
Define How Meta Ads Converts Third-Party Data
Select the Meta Ads actions to define the action used for third-party conversions in the Segment Intelligence.
Select Who Can Use Segment Intelligence
Assign permissions to enable users to set up and use Segment Intelligence.
